reviewText: Great service! There is nothing that needs to be improved at all. Will buy from again sometime in the near future.

This movie was great!! I am a great big fan of the Naruto Shippuden "saga" and will avidly & vehemently support mostly all that it presents! The plot and events of this movie cause it to be a great addition to my collection of Naruto movies!
I had already had given what I through of this movie that I already have it in English form on DVD.
like the english verison this one is suoer. it goes to showe just how much naruto has grown and whgo he will protcet and love.
the movie come before it due date and the desk was in great cond the case was a little bit up but that was fine i don't really care about that. It plays great even in my crapy PS2
The story is excellent! The English dub version of this is out also. It's titled Naruto Shippuden The Will of Fire! It' excellent! With Maile Flanagan and the cast!
This was a great purchase from this seller all around from the fast delivery to the awesome item. I recommend this seller if you are a Naruto Shippuden fan.
Received well ahead of schedule. Have watched it with my dad and my anime club and truly enjoy it. A lot of my friends have asked to borrow it and have enjoyed it.

The cover of the DVD case was a bonus. Everything was in Japanese but if you're American and like subtitles you'll love it. Some of the translation was off and laughable. Like When Kakashi say "Scum" the movie editor translated into "trashes" Weird! The stories plot stunning, this is a movie that you ninja-fools would die for.
THE movie was great and awesome, especially the end. But the subs where kinda crappy, but its worth getting. This movie is a must get for fans.
